channel.title: My Goals
channel.description:
I'm a noob I know, but my goal is to get every one of my skills to it's next ten, meaning that if it's like level 50 right now, I want it to be 60, if its level 37, I want it to be 40, I'm sure you get it. Support and suggestions would be nice, I'll have a chart of all my levels, as well as picture progression. Here is my starting position. 3-31-13 [IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/28qsy7p.png[/img]
Attack: 72 Strength: 66 Defense: 66 Range: 35 Prayer: 49 Magic: 65 Runecrafting: 60 Construction: 50 - FINISHED Dungeoneering: 36 HP: 68 Agility: 41 Herblore: 40 Thieving: 33 Crafting: 57 Fletching: 50 Slayer: 42 Hunter: 14 Mining: 57 Smithing: 55 Fishing: 53 Cooking: 65 Firemaking: 74 Woodcutting: 77 Farming: 17 Summoning: 19
Thanks guys.
